THOUGHT: For this task family, I want to explore the intersection of computational creativity and literary analysis. Given the success of previous tasks involving interdisciplinary knowledge and creative problem-solving, I believe a task that combines natural language processing techniques with literary theory could be both challenging and revealing of an LLM's capabilities. This task will require the model to not only understand complex literary concepts but also apply them in a creative and analytical manner. I think this task will be novel and different from the previously generated tasks, as it focuses specifically on computational approaches to literary analysis.

